Package com.nba.application.objectRepository

Class NBASixersPageObjects

java.lang.Object
com.nba.application.objectRepository.NBASixersPageObjects
public class NBASixersPageObjects extends Object
Repository class for object locators of the NBA Sixers page. This class holds the locators for various elements on the NBA Sixers page.
